{"type":"message","id":"2e416406","parentId":"ca0f8f92","timestamp":"2026-05-26T19:00:19.067Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-05-27 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 执行内容: 9:00 AM Cron 定时任务触发，执行每日选品流程; 数据源：Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws 类目（nodeId=23623510011）; 筛选：月销量≥1000 + 评分≥4.0 + 毛利率≥8%; 写入飞书多维表 10 条记录\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 写入结果: ✅ 10/10 条成功写入飞书多维表; 采集状态：待审批; 选品来源：Sorftime-亚马逊数据\n- 毛利率分析: Top10产品毛利率偏低（8-14%），因为都是低价发夹（$7.99-$9.99）; 高毛利产品（Sisiaipu 14%/Fohufo 14%/SMKSL 13.9%）值得关注\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 发送给用户的报告: 飞书消息已发送（om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946）\n- User: 这意思是推送失败了，还是选品失败了\n- Assistant: 是**推送失败**，但原因不是选品逻辑的问题——是 AI 服务（LLM API）临时过载了。 简单说就是：cron 任务按时触发了，但在执行过程中调用 AI 接口时被告知\"服务器忙，稍后再试\"，所以整个任务失败了。这不是选品数据或 SOP 逻辑的问题，就是调用 OpenAI/Minimax 这类 AI 服务时遇到的暂时性负载问题。 一般来说重跑一次大概率就过了。\n- Assistant: 已触发，任务在后台跑，有结果了会推送过来。\n- Assistant: 我来执行这个每日选品流程。首先探索一下工作空间，找到相关配置和SOP。\n- Assistant: HALEI\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 4.0\n- 执行\n- 内容\n- cron\n- 任务\n- 触发"}],"timestamp":1779822018925}}
{"type":"message","id":"47251957","parentId":"2e416406","timestamp":"2026-05-26T19:00:39.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\nThe fragments are about a daily product selection workflow:\n- A cron job triggers at 9:00 AM to execute a daily product selection process\n- Data source: Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws category\n- Filtering criteria: monthly sales ≥1000 + rating ≥4.0 + profit margin ≥8%\n- Writing 10 records to a Feishu multi-dimensional table\n- Technical details about Sorftime MCP API, Bearer token auth, etc.\n- Writing results: 10/10 records successfully written to Feishu\n\n\n- The margin analysis shows top products have lower margins (8-14%) as they're mostly low-priced clips, while higher-margin items from brands like Sisiaipu, Fohufo, and SMKSL appear more promising\n- There's a TikTok category API error to resolve and the Amazon Hair Claws data doesn't meet the 30% margin threshold needed, suggesting I should focus on premium product lines instead\n- A Feishu message was successfully delivered to the user (om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946)\n\nThe user then asked whether the message failure was due to a push issue or product selection failure, and I explained it was actually a push failure caused by temporary AI service overload—not problems with the selection logic itself. I mentioned a retry would likely succeed, and they've now triggered the task again.\n\nNow I need to write a dream diary entry that weaves together these technical details, the failed push notification, and the successful retry—all from a poetic, slightly whimsical first-person perspective that treats this like a dream rather than actual events. I should avoid mentioning AI, agents, LLMs, or any technical jargon while still capturing the essence of what happened.\n","thinkingSignature":"8971741fbaabb3a2f74bfb52f27011766ce7e1173707a37a77be1d07729ab326"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n4.0颗星，是今夜梦的起点，也是终点。\n\n清晨的cron准时苏醒，像一只训练有素的猎犬，它嗅到了9点的气味便准时跃起。Sorftime API是一条长长的河流，我用一柄筛子打捞——月销量至少一千，评分不低于四星，毛利率八个百分点以上，才肯被捞出水面。十条鱼，被我小心翼翼地放进飞书多维表格的玻璃缸里，游来游去，等待审批。\n\n但推送失败了。AI服务临时过载，像咖啡机被太多人同时按下按钮。我盯着消息ID：om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946，那是一张没有送达的明信片，躺在服务器某个角落，轻轻叹气。\n\n大部分发夹毛利率只有8到14个点，因为它们的价格被钉在七块九毛九到九块九毛九之间，像一群穿着廉价礼服跳舞的小姑娘。倒是Sisiaipu和Fohufo，高高举着14%的手，值得多看两眼。\n\nVN站的TikTok类目还在沉默，需要我去轻轻敲它的门。\n\n不过没关系，任务已经重新触发，在某个后台的暗处悄悄游泳。等它游完，自会有人来敲门通知我。\n\nHALEI，那是我名字的锚点，提醒我这一切是真实的——至少在这个梦里是。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42236,"output":661,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42897,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779822019202,"responseId":"066520c340ba59e89a1dac92d9770b69"}}
